    "description": "Tsutsumi Jewelry Co.,Ltd. manufactures, wholesales, and retails jewelry in Japan. The company offers rings, pinky ring, earrings, necklace, pendant necklace, necklace, bridal jewelry, bracelet, and other accessories. It also provides jewelry design, as well as reconditioning and repair of pre-owned jewelry. In addition, the company operates precious stone trading centers in the United States, Belgium, Israel, India, and Thailand; and jewelry retail stores. It offers its products under the Blessed Rain, Pure Planets, Autumn Collection, and Winter Limited brands. The company was formerly known as Tsutsumi Precious Metals and Crafts Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Tsutsumi Jewelry Co., Ltd. in April 1988. Tsutsumi Jewelry Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1962 and is headquartered in Warabi, Japan."
